        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figs. 30-38. Borolinus minutus: 30, head and pronotum in dorsal view; 31, aedeagus in dorsal view; 32, aedeagus in lateral view; 33, 9th abdominal sternite of male; 34, left half of 9th abdominal sternite of female; 35, mandibles; 36, 9th and 10th abdominal tergites of male; 37, labrum; 38, mentum. Scale bars: Figs. 30, 35 = 1 mm; Figs. 31-34, 36-38 = 0.25 mm." ;
